code: import ICAL from"ical";import axios from"axios";import{DayPilot,DayPilotCalendar}from"daypilot-pro-react";const URL="http://localhost:4000/events";export const getEvents=async(start,end)=>{const startDate=new DayPilot.Date(start);const endDate=new DayPilot.Date(end);const response=await axios.get("".concat(URL,"?start=").concat(startDate,"&end=").concat(endDate));return response.data;};
